<self-uri xlink:href="http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_arttext&amp;pid=S0103-40142015000300019&amp;lng=en&amp;nrm=iso"></self-uri><self-uri xlink:href="http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_abstract&amp;pid=S0103-40142015000300019&amp;lng=en&amp;nrm=iso"></self-uri><self-uri xlink:href="http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_pdf&amp;pid=S0103-40142015000300019&amp;lng=en&amp;nrm=iso"></self-uri><abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="pt"><p><![CDATA[resumo A poesia de Orides Fontela se afasta com notável liberdade de inflexões dominantes da modernidade. O que sobretudo a caracteriza, além de seu rigor formal extremo, é a interrogação permanente sobre o nosso destino e a figuração de nexos simbólicos entre as experiências vividas e sua projeção transcendente.]]></p></abstract>
<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[abstract The poetry of Orides Fontela departs with remarkable freedom from the dominant inflections of modernity. Besides an extreme formal rigor, its foremost trait is the permanent questioning of our destiny and the portrayal of symbolic nexuses between the experiences one lives and their transcendental projection.]]></p></abstract>
